TopicTitle: Jamie xx: Gosh - Music Video Tribute

Articles.Content:
Hey all, just made a music video in KSP for a recent song I made. It's a tribute/remake of the video for Jamie XX's song Gosh. I love the original so wanted to try my hand at making something similar.
https://youtu.be/HGRrBS20fqs

My song isn't quite the same style but I think it suits nonetheless. Chuck me a sub if you like it and feel free to ask any questions here or on the video.

Also a shout-out to www.youtube.com/ShadowZone for making the craft files available for the ring stations, I wouldn't have had the patience to put that together.

https://youtu.be/MYA7a740Jbw - Ring station build.

Enjoy
